<br>
In fact I think I started soloing these things at 34 or so. I had to use root/heal for some fights and I would always end up with 2 bubbles of health but the experience was well worth the downtime. The earrings also commanded a nice price back then and it made the lack of loot worth it. <br>
<br>
Good thing about these cats is they hit fast for the level and sometimes they will hit hard too. This allows you to get your defensive skills up pretty quickly and also allows you to judge when you are going to win a fight and when you will lose one (extremely important for soloing). Basically if you start early enough these cats will allow you to test your limits.<br>
<br>
Tramaus Voronadil<br>
